in cream too.

95
00:05:00,218 --> 00:05:03,179
In cr... Oh, why do they do that?
It's weird.

96
00:05:03,263 --> 00:05:09,394
- And Maeve. Even Maeve's got a friend.
- [inhales deeply] - I wanna swing. - But you've been swinging this whole time.

97
00:05:09,477 --> 00:05:12,105
