- That kid's kind of an asshole.

98
00:05:12,188 --> 00:05:13,398
She definitely bums me out.

99
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:16,276
- Oh, hey.
- Buddy!

100
00:05:16,359 --> 00:05:19,404
- Oh, look at you. What a vision in floral.
- [Charlie] Hey!

101
00:05:19,487 --> 00:05:20,387
