124
00:06:21,591 --> 00:06:23,593
What is execution?

125
00:06:24,094 --> 00:06:26,846
Dessert. Everybody, dessert.

126
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,431
I'll tell you later.

127
00:06:28,932 --> 00:06:30,599
- [guests chattering]
- [pop music playing]

128
00:06:30,642 --> 00:06:32,602
[chuckling]

129
