131
00:06:42,237 --> 00:06:43,277
- [chuckles]
- Are you o...

132
00:06:43,321 --> 00:06:44,864
[all chuckling, chattering]

133
00:06:46,449 --> 00:06:47,699
[Diane] I know. And that's how I...

134
